<p><strong><font size=\"4\" color=\"#800080\" face=\"Arial\">Terms of Service </font></strong></p>
<font size=\"+1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial;\"><font size=\"+1\">Realty SignPost LLC is a real estate signpost RENTAL and INSTALLATION SERVICE Company. We strive to provide Fast, Dependable and Professional service to the real estate agents of the Greater Washington DC metro area. The following Terms and Conditions are provided to help foster a mutually beneficial business relationship.</font></span></font><font size=\"+1\">&nbsp; </font>
<p><a href=\"#top\">^ Back to Top</a></p>
<p><font size=\"+1\">GENERAL OVERVIEW:<a name=\"general\"></a>&nbsp; Realty SignPost provides and installs a wood or PVC signpost at a customer specificied address for the purposes of advertising that property for sale or rent. Signpost rental period is the lesser of 120 days from date of installation, or 7 days from the date the property sale closes or the listing is withdrawn. Realty SignPost also provides sign panel storage and installation services, as well as the opportunity to order &lsquo;add on&rsquo; items, like brochure boxes and Power Punch riders, to assist the agent in selling or renting the property.</font></p>
<p><font size=\"+1\"><br /> </font><a href=\"#top\">^ Back to Top </a><font size=\"+1\"><br /> <br /> ORDER COMPLETION TIME FRAME:<a id=\"ordercompletion\" name=\"ordercompletion\"></a><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Realty SignPost policy is to complete all orders within TWO business days, excluding extreme weather days, if a complete and accurate order is received by 5PM for our core Northern Virginia service area. Please note that business days do NOT include weekends or Federal Holidays. <br /> The first business day is the next business day after the order is received. This means that an order placed on Tuesday by 5PM will be completed on Wednesday or Thursday and orders placed between 5 p.m. Thursday and 5 p.m. Sunday will be scheduled for Monday or Tuesday the following week.<br /> For Orders in our Core Maryland and Washington DC area, there is a THREE business day installation window. This means that an order placed on Tuesday by 5PM will be completed on Wednesday, Thursday or Friday. <br /> For orders in our Extended Service Areas, there is a FIVE business day installation window.</font><font size=\"+1\"><br /> </font></p>
<p><a href=\"#top\">^ Back to Top </a></p>
<p><font size=\"+1\"><br /> SERVICE AREAS:<a id=\"serviceareas\" name=\"serviceareas\"></a><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Our CORE Northern Virginia service area covers all of Arlington, Fairfax, Prince William and eastern Loudon counties.&nbsp; Our CORE MD and DC service area covers all of Montgomery County, Northern Prince George\'s County, Southern Frederick County, and parts of Howard and Anne Arundel counties in MD and all of Washington DC.</font></p>
<p><a href=\"service_area_core.php\">Click here to view our CORE Service Area on Google Maps.</a></p>
<p><font size=\"+1\"><br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Our EXTENDED Service area includes Clarke, Culpeper, Fauquier, Frederick, western Loudoun, Stafford, Spotsylvania and Warren counties in VA, northern Frederick and Washington counties in MD, Berkeley and Jefferson counties in WV, and Adams, Franklin and Fulton counties in PA. An additional installer travel allowance may apply for orders in our extended service areas. Please e-mail the address to info@realtysignpost.com before placing install order to determine exact surcharge.<br /> Note: Western Loudoun is defined as the area west of 659/Gum Spring Rd to the Dulles Greenway, and the areas west and north of the Leesburg city limits. </font></p>
